sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as 客户端
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant API as Go秒杀接入服务
    participant Redis as Redis Cluster
    participant MQ as RocketMQ
    participant Consumer as 订单消费者
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Query as 查询服务

    Client->>Gateway: POST /seckill<br/>request_id
    Gateway->>API: 已鉴权请求
    API->>Redis: Lua预占库存
    Redis-->>API: RESERVED + reservation_id

    API->>MQ: 发送OrderCreate<br/>message_id
    MQ-->>API: Broker ACK
    API-->>Client: QUEUING

    MQ->>Consumer: 投递消息
    Consumer->>PG: 本地事务<br/>Inbox + 最终库存 + Order + Outbox
    PG-->>Consumer: COMMIT成功
    Consumer-->>MQ: ACK
    Consumer->>Redis: 更新reservation查询结果

    Client->>Query: GET /seckill/result?request_id=...
    Query->>Redis: 查询短期结果
    Redis-->>Query: ORDER_CREATED
    Query-->>Client: order_id
